{"type": "article", "id": 32749, "title": "要关上这个闹钟，你得帮它倒个立｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-28T23:25:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 3255, "name": "Menu"}, {"id": 16057, "name": "Norm Architects"}, {"id": 24757, "name": "Typical Organization"}, {"id": 33284, "name": "KÖLLEN"}, {"id": 33285, "name": "Studiomateriality"}, {"id": 33286, "name": "Nytec"}, {"id": 33287, "name": "Encode Ring"}, {"id": 31108, "name": "Samuel Wilkinson"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 11, "praise_count": 187, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160928213712xKa8dVbEOZCW2vT4.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Audiowear by Nytec Inc.</h3><p>由美国的 <a href=\"http://www.nytec.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nytec</a> 公司带来的这款 Audiowear 蓝牙音频设备可不仅仅是一个看上去相当酷炫的耳机，你或许可以从它的命名猜出它的另一个“身份”，那就是可穿戴音响。如果你本来使用的是它的“耳机模式”，当你从头上摘下时它就会自动展开，转变为“音响模式”，此时中间的部分刚好可以用来倚靠手机或是平板设备。当你想用耳机的时候，只要施力将它拗弯即可。这款概念设计产品是 2016 红点设计奖的<a href=\"http://www.red-dot.sg/en/online-exhibition/audiowear/\" rel=\"nofollow\">获奖作品</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609282140260iSCvFoA38V4uGaq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928214025gSfP2LO4DB3d8Eyw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609282140252DxVJIuXoWGkLhOE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609282140264VI0exkCzYm3sN1W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928214026N6VG1ikB8ZSleFYK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928214027TF6CJx5uam4pGQ7A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Brace by Samuel Wilkinson</h3><p>在今年的伦敦设计节上，设计师 <a href=\"https://encodering.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Samuel Wilkinson</a> 带来了他通过传统的蒸汽曲木加工技术制作的木椅 Brace 系列。它由曲木以及一块木制座位构成，拱形结构不仅看上去相当极简，还充满了一种圆润的美感。在 Wilkinson 看来，蒸汽曲木加工能够直接将小尺寸木材弯曲的特点呈现出来，而且相当环保经济，能够有效地减少对木材的浪费。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213945xvIoi9JUdpcg5Fma.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.780457\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213946n94wzLbDSFJtYx3I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.727157\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609282139461hWUZP7er5Y8EziV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667482\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>值得一提的是，Wilkinson 在展示时还特意制作一个名为 Offcut （边角料）的装置，在边长 3 米的立方体黑色金属框内用白线吊起了超过四千块从曲木加工厂收集来的边角料，加上四周的照明装置，它们就像是茧一样把木椅包裹起来。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928214006buE5GUlzhnwFvQD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.775061\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928214006WNogC4PEVM1QhA6y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.364303\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928214007pbk12U6aDRPKgFlu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.407090\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>KÖLLEN bookshelf by KÖLLEN</h3><p>          </p><p>如果你偏好挂墙式书架，并且对灵活度有所要求的话，由四个西班牙设计系学生带来的这款 KÖLLEN 书架会是一个不错的选择。书架由一片片 2 厘米厚的桦木胶合板构成，水平位置下可以用来放置物品，最大承重为 30 千克。如果你想换一种风格，只要把它们旋转到与地面垂直即可，这个状态下木板组成的起伏的形状是团队根据阿尔卑斯山脉特意设计的。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/kollen/kollen-the-interactive-bookshelf-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，最低价为 325 欧元，如果你需要定制颜色，价格为 370 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928222328VoikZq40wbYQRmlK.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.513333\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928222326JDUhlQyW2I9NkwtA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332353\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928222326mNHVy312UYGb7pPJ.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Encode Ring by Encode Ring Co.</h3><p>你或许还记得我们曾经介绍过一系列<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/27706.html\">可以根据风向定制的首饰</a>，今天介绍的 Encode Ring 来自日本，是一款根据人声进行定制的戒指。如果你想为特别的人送上一份独一无二的礼物，可以通过它的<a href=\"https://encodering.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>进行定制，戒指起伏的形状就是根据你录下的三秒钟音频的声波制作而成的。Encode Ring 有不锈钢、金、银以及白金四种材质可选，售价从 32400 日元起，制作时间在一个月左右。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213806urzTVaq6WdOcNx7A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.737500\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213806MOde7zqE048fBiZh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213806BEUcRrsXZpMJ5vfV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213806IzYB38QKVug0ty6L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609282138065wZkUeaMoKS4iCf8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609282138061cQ5MiLsNYfT4Uka.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Tumbler Alarm Clock by Norm Architects</h3><p>为了让你起床，有些闹钟设计在开关上下足了功夫，如果你对这类需要你费尽心思的产品并不感冒但又想要一个有些不一样的设计，这款名为 Tumbler 的闹钟或许会让你会心一笑。它由丹麦的 <a href=\"http://www.normcph.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Norm Architects</a> 和 <a href=\"http://www.menu.as/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Menu</a> 共同打造，响起的时候你需要将它倒置才能关上闹铃——依靠内部的机械结构，它并不会倾倒，而是稳稳地站在桌面上。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213843XlgtQkeuCKf3zFrA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213845hVPtvKZ6bmSgnWAT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213846ifsjqw6g8dUM2KDz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213848c3epNRQnrvduH8KI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.383088\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Studiomateriality Scarves by Typical Organization</h3><p>在卖丝巾这件事上，希腊设计工作室 <a href=\"http://typical-organization.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Typical Organization</a> 为工作坊 <a href=\"http://www.studiomateriality.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Studiomateriality</a> 设计的方案并不是将它们挂在架子上或者用纸包好放进盒子中：绚丽多彩的丝巾被放进了白底黑字的罐头中，抽出时就好像打开了一罐彩色的颜料，感觉相当奇妙。除了丝巾的基本信息以外，工作室还在铁罐上留下了不少有趣的句子，你还能发现引自超现实主义艺术家勒内·马格里特（René Magritte）的那句“这不是一支烟斗”。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016092821373520KJOc5Fnq6Ad3Wh.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213735XoMD3AVn8m9fYrgE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.757000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213735Xc1FAZ6omxHq2TYB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213735zbDLK2ZnlNriBp6R.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160928213734pAE1iF6jO2stnoH8.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}